# 🗂️ Task Manager App

Task Manager App is a modern, vibrant, and fully-responsive productivity tool — built entirely with **vanilla HTML, CSS, and JavaScript**. It allows users to manage tasks efficiently with multi-user profiles, live analytics, stunning themes, and image exports. Everything runs locally in your browser and can be deployed instantly on **Vercel**.

---

## ⚡ Try It Now

👉 **Organize your tasks effortlessly:**  
[Launch Task Manager App Online 🚀](https://task-manager-app-iota-wheat.vercel.app/)

---

