---

## 🚀 Features

- 🎨 **Multiple Themes:** Six beautiful color palettes — Blue, Forest, Sunset, Berry, Ocean, Rose.  
- 👤 **Multi-User Profiles:** Register, switch, and personalize with 8 avatars.  
- 📝 **Advanced Task Management:** Tasks can include descriptions, priority, category, due dates, time estimates, and progress tracking.  
- 🔍 **Filters & Sorting:** Live filter by category/status and sort by name, priority, or date.  
- 📊 **Analytics Dashboard:** Visualize completion trends, overdue tasks, and category breakdowns using Chart.js.  
- 🖼️ **Export as PNG:** Download your task board or profile as a high-resolution image.  
- 📱 **Mobile & Accessible:** Optimized for touch, keyboard shortcuts, and screen readers.  
- 🔒 **Private & Offline:** All data stays local — no cloud uploads or tracking.

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

| Technology     | Usage                          |
|----------------|--------------------------------|
| HTML/CSS/JS    | Core structure and functionality |
| Chart.js       | Interactive charts & analytics |
| html2canvas    | Export boards/profiles as PNG  |

---

## 📦 How It Works

1. Open the [live demo](https://task-manager-app-iota-wheat.vercel.app/) or `index.html` locally.  
2. Register a profile with your name, email, and avatar.  
3. Create, update, and organize tasks with detailed fields.  
4. Filter, search, and sort tasks in real-time.  
5. Export your lists or profile as a PNG image.  
6. Manage everything offline — no login required.

---

## 📁 File Structure

```bash
task-manager-app/
├── index.html                # Entry point & main UI
├── css/
│   └── style.css             # Theme-based styling
├── js/
│   ├── app.js                # Core app logic & flows
│   ├── ui.js                 # UI rendering, chart handling, exports
│   └── storage.js            # Multi-user persistence with localStorage
├── libs/
│   └── html2canvas.min.js    # PNG export library
├── screenshots/
│   ├── tasks-Rani Malik-2025-10-01.png
│   └── profile-Rani Malik-2025-10-01.png
└── README.md                 # This file


